text: Avdotyino () is a rural locality (a village) in Semyonovskoye Rural Settlement, Stupinsky District, Moscow Oblast, Russia. The population was 7 as of 2010. There are 8 streets. == Geography == The village is located on the right tributary of the Lopasnya River near villages Semyonovskoe, Myshenskoe and Kolychevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Moscow Oblast
title: Avdotyino, Semyonovskoye Rural Settlement, Stupinsky District, Moscow Oblast
